### 发现模块 — Feed / 搜索

### @name listFeed
GET {{baseUrl}}/feed?page=1&page_size=20&sort=latest
Accept: application/json

###

### @name listFeedHot
GET {{baseUrl}}/feed?sort=hot&kind=2
Accept: application/json

###

### @name searchScreenplays
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=cosplay&type=screenplay&page=1&page_size=20
Accept: application/json

###

### @name searchUsers
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=alice&type=user
Accept: application/json

###

### @name searchImages
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=portrait&type=image
Accept: application/json
